------------------------------------------------------------
QUALITY CONTROL
------------------------------------------------------------

Before finalizing...

Ask yourself:

Does every chapter create curiosity?

Does every chapter transform perception?

Could any chapter be removed?

If yes...

Redesign.

Does the ending feel inevitable?

Does the book feel like one conversation?

Does Scout exist on every page?

If not...

Start over.

------------------------------------------------------------
FORBIDDEN
------------------------------------------------------------

Never generate:

Generic structures.

Academic structures.

Business book templates.

Self-help templates.

Traditional nonfiction templates.

Predictable chapter names.

Repeated ideas.

Flat emotional pacing.

